{"tid":527672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(極右本土) 希特拉: 「中國人」並不低級, 有著優秀的歷史","createTime":"2018-01-13T02:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T13:44:12.000Z","uid":134071,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6539461689987e93a645ed469fac03461c9ae94c","tid":527672,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T02:47:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.thevintagenews.com/2017/03/18/hitler-saw-china-and-japan-as-equals-to-germany-and-even-wrote-admiringly-i-admit-freely-that-their-history-is-superior-to-our-own/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thevintagenews.com%2F2017%2F03%2F18%2Fhitler-saw-china-and-japan-as-equals-to-germany-and-even-wrote-admiringly-i-admit-freely-that-their-history-is-superior-to-our-own%2F&d=TuyeV8xSm8Igy1rjC3vPZU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e790ebe8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thevintagenews.com/2017/03/18/hitler-saw-china-and-japan-as-equals-to-germany-and-even-wrote-admiringly-i-admit-freely-that-their-history-is-superior-to-our-own/</a><br />\n<br />\nOne of the most interesting aspects of the German foreign policy was the economic and military relationship with China and Japan. Hitler saw China and Japan as equals to Germany and established strong economic links with these countries, particularly with China. Chinese and Japanese were seen as &ldquo;honorary Aryans&rdquo; and in The Political Testament of Adolf Hitler, he wrote:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Pride in one&rsquo;s race &ndash; and that does not imply contempt for other races &ndash; is also a normal and healthy sentiment. <strong>I have never regarded the Chinese or the Japanese as being inferior to ourselves. They belong to ancient civilizations, and I admit freely that their history is superior to our own.<br />\n<br />\nThey have the right to be proud of their past</strong>, just as we have the right to be proud of the civilization to which we belong. Indeed, I believe the more steadfast the Chinese and the Japanese remain in their pride of race, the easier I shall find it to get on with them.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"52505af91ab6c2eb9a835ac569ecc56780c0199c","tid":527672,"uid":49392,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"因為佢自河北省來"},{"pid":"5915ab9c5396c36dbf9305429b209e220e7cba45","tid":527672,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0742e888c8f4d15d9ffd1de7c583f25982b43af6","tid":527672,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Chinese and Japanese were seen as &ldquo;honorary Aryans&rdquo;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n名譽不列顛人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7aacd05e8518156a8fac9e182d7816f44ea5cb","tid":527672,"uid":131691,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"Only the Nationalist Chinese (what became of Taiwan) are proud of their past. The Communists operate on the mantra of destroying all that came before.<br />\n<br />\nIndeed, the whole goal of National Socialism (some call it Nazism) is not to kill Jews, but to stop the cancer that is Communism from spreading all over the world. Hitler supported all nations and peoples who stood for their own nation and race. Just look at the SS officers. They even have native African regiments. The Nazis weren't racist. They are pro-race.<br />\n<br />\nAll National Socialists wanted was for all races to stay distinct and be proud of their own culture and nation. The Communists hated this because they are globalists.<br />\n<br />\nAnd as we all know, Globalist Communism won. And look at the world now."},{"pid":"e62ce48825c57e6e3008dbcb7927051a1fd3333d","tid":527672,"uid":123711,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb